data.description: SELLER WILLING TO HELP WITH 7K FOR YOUR CLOSING COSTS - A PROFESSIONAL WILL ALSO WASH THE CARPET TO MAKE IT LIKE NEW, Home, sweet home! Discover this gorgeous 4-bedroom property nestled in the Sundance Community! You'll be greeted by a charming interior featuring soothing palette throughout, neutral tile flooring, plush carpet in all the right places, & arched doorways. The well-kept kitchen boasts ample cabinetry, backsplash windows, recessed lighting, & built-in appliances to make meal prep a bliss. The versatile loft is the perfect spot for an entertainment area or game room. Primary bedroom enjoys a private bathroom with dual sinks & a convenient walk-in closet. The spacious backyard including a cozy covered patio is waiting for you! Don't miss out
